{"type": "article", "id": 20752, "title": "丹麦Dubokk极简家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-15T07:17:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115145VepKF9qH4oREnNQm.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是丹麦的设计工作室 Dubokk 带来的家具系列，包括花瓶、杂志架和茶几。花瓶已近似一个玻璃杯，一个支架连接着底座，可以将花插在中间的圆环里，也方便固定。植物的茎叶就完全暴露在视线内，很通透。茶几是由黑色的金属框和玻璃桌面组成，桌面和抽屉的支撑结构都圆弧形的，像是大小两种套在了一起，有很强的线条感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115143Hp7ur8zDKUWfTVsX.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115143q0l5a9dyMSvUFCXG.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115144mCKslxQq5rIiAZj4.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115144zUjoFA035iJWfSpB.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}